  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> is a <b>SME<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->1000000<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->5.50<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹55 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->2000<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->March 6, 2024</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->March 11, 2024</b>.</p><p>Kfin Technologies Limited<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE SME<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO opens on March 6, 2024 and closes on March 11, 2024.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the lot size of Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> <b>lot size is <!-- -->2000</b>, and the <b>minimum amount required is <span>₹1,10,000</span></b>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply for Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>You can apply in <!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> online using either <a href=\"/article/upi-payment-option-ipo-application-explained/382/\">UPI</a> or ASBA as a payment method. ASBA IPO application is available in the net banking of your bank account. UPI IPO application is offered by brokers who don't offer banking services. Read more detail about applying IPO online through <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Review\"><b>Zerodha</b></a>, <a href=\"/broker/upstox/ipo/33/\" title=\"Upstox IPO Review\">Upstox</a>, <a href=\"/broker/5paisa/ipo/4/\" title=\"5Paisa IPO Review\">5Paisa</a>, <a href=\"/broker/edelweiss_broking/ipo/34/\" title=\"Nuvama IPO Review\">Nuvama</a>, <a href=\"/broker/hdfc-securities/ipo/6/\" title=\"HDFC Bank IPO Review\">HDFC Bank</a>, and <a href=\"/broker/sbi-capital/ipo/19/\" title=\"SBI Capital IPO Review\">SBI Bank</a>.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When is Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO allotment?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The finalization of Basis of Allotment for <!-- -->Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> will be done on <!-- -->Tuesday, March 12, 2024<!-- -->, and the allotted shares will be credited to your demat account by <!-- -->Wednesday, March 13, 2024<!-- -->. Check the <a href=\"/ipo_allotment_status/koura-fine-diamond-jewelry-ipo/1669/\" title=\"Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO Allotment Status\">Koura Fine Diamond Jewelry IPO<!-- --> allotment status</a>.</p></div>"
